{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MediaStream()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/MediaStream","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Media_Capture_and_Streams_API\">Media Capture and Streams API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><em><code>MediaStream()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/active\"><code>active</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/id\"><code>id</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/addTrack\"><code>addTrack()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/clone\"><code>clone()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/getAudioTracks\"><code>getAudioTracks()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/getTrackById\"><code>getTrackById()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/getTracks\"><code>getTracks()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/getVideoTracks\"><code>getVideoTracks()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>事件</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/addtrack_event\"><code>addtrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/removetrack_event\"><code>removetrack</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Media Capture and Streams 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices\"><code>MediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>VideoStreamTrack</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>构造函数**<code>MediaStream()</code>** 返回新建的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a> 实例，该实例作为媒体流的内容的集合载体，其可能包含多个媒体数据轨，每个数据轨则由一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a> 对象表示。如果给出相应参数，在指定的数据轨则被添加到新的流中。否则，该流中不包含任何数据轨。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>newStream <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nnewStream <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>stream<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nnewStream <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MediaStream</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>tracks<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"stream\"><code>stream</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>这是另一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a> 对象，其数据轨会被自动添加到新建的流中。且这些数据轨不会从原流中移除，即变成了两条流共享的数据。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"tracks\"><code>tracks</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>这是 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack\"><code>MediaStreamTrack</code></a> 对象的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a> 类型的成员，代表了每一个添加到流中的数据轨。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>新建的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a> 对象，会包含创建时已给的数据轨内容，若没有给定任何数据轨则内容为空。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#dom-mediastream-constructor","title":"Media Capture and Streams"}],"query":"api.MediaStream.MediaStream"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaStream.MediaStream","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/MediaStream/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"构造函数**MediaStream()** 返回新建的 MediaStream 实例，该实例作为媒体流的内容的集合载体，其可能包含多个媒体数据轨，每个数据轨则由一个 MediaStreamTrack 对象表示。如果给出相应参数，在指定的数据轨则被添加到新的流中。否则，该流中不包含任何数据轨。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MediaStream()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MediaStream()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/mediastream/mediastream","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/mediastream/mediastream/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream","title":"媒体流 (MediaStream)"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaStream/MediaStream","title":"MediaStream()"}],"pageTitle":"MediaStream() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}